snippet.title: Pitch Deck Devlog #01- Player Abilities and Enemies
snippet.description:
Thanks For Watching!

Pitch Deck is a game about reverting corrupted corporate workers back into humans and freeing them from their corporate shackles by using augmentation gloves with sick powers! 

The desks and the room types are all randomly procedurally generated with details like computer types, props, tools, etc. 

TRY THE DEMO!
https://bit.ly/pitch-deck-game
